          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1666696273045-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepperoni has started to brown, add the <strong>chopped cavolo nero </strong>and <strong>sliced garlic</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the cavolo nero has wilted</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1666696277086-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1666696277086-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1666696277086-x700.jpg",
